com.github.dakusui.jcunitx.metamodel

Interface ParameterSpace


  • public interface ParameterSpace

    A test input parameter space. It consists of parameters and constraints over them.

    This interface defines the user-facing model of the system under test.

      • encodeSeeds

        static List<AArray> encodeSeeds(ParameterSpace parameterSpace,
                                List<AArray> seeds)

        Encodes the given seeds into its internal representation. NOTE: that the seeds need to be complete, that means all the parameters in a seed must have a concrete value. This is a limitation of the current version of JCUnit, because in the CIT area "seeding" is done for the

        Parameters:
        parameterSpace - The parameter space in which the seeds are defined.
        seeds - A set of test cases from which the final test suite is generated.
        Returns:
        A list of encoded seeds.
